      ConnectorDefinitionBuilder addConnector(String name, String connectorId, String version, ConnectorEvent activationEvent)
      Add a connector on this element

      Must also add connector dependencies and connector implementation descriptor

      Parameters:

      connectorId - The id of the Connector definition (connector implementation added in org.bonitasoft.engine.bpm.bar.BusinessArchive must match this id in definitionId
      version - The version of the Connector definition
      activationEvent - ConnectorEvent on which the connector will be triggered
      Returns:
